nking and financial products and services to personal business and public sector customers in the united kingdom the company operates through retail banking commercial banking and global corporate banking segments its deposit products include interestbearing and noninterestbearing current and demand accounts savings accounts and time deposits the company offers residential mortgage loans personal loans credit cards consumer finance business banking products and overdrafts as well as insurance policies it also provides treasury invoice discounting cash transmission trade finance asset finance and commercial real estate and social  santander uk plc provides a range of banking and financial products and services to personal business and public sector customers in the united kingdom the company operates through retail banking commercial banking and global corporate banking segments its deposit products include interestbearing and noninterestbearing current and demand accounts savings accounts and time deposits the company offers residential mortgage loans personal loans credit cards consumer finance business banking products and overdrafts as well as insurance policies it also provides treasury invoice discounting cash transmission trade finance asset finance and commercial real estate and social housing loans currency fluctuations management and interest rate risk protection products and capital markets finance arrangements and specialist trade finance solutions the company operates through a network of  branches and  corporate business centers as well as through atm telephony digital mobile internet and intermediary channels santander uk plc was incorporated in  and is based in london the united kingdom santander uk plc is a subsidiary of santander uk group holdings plc detailed description  triton squareregent’s placelondon  nw anunited kingdomfounded in  employees phone     wwwsantandercouk key executives for santander uk plc mr nathan mark bostock chief executive o