banking subsidiary santander private banking operates in jersey sixdigit account sort codes are used in the range between xx to xx sort codes for accounts formerly held by alliance  leicester use the range  to  in  santander launched the uks first current account without fees including unauthorised overdrafts for its current and future mortgage customers customers are not charged fees for using santanders automated teller machines in spain which traditionally would incur fees for transactions in a foreign currency sponsorshipsedit santanderbranded bicycles in london santander has sponsored the mclaren formula one team since  and is also the title sponsor of the british grand prix santander said its sponsorship of mclaren had raised its brand awareness in the uk from  to  percent the bank announced a second team sponsorship with scuderia ferrari in  golfer rory mcilroy signed a sponsorship agreement with the bank in september  and in  it was announced that british athlete jessica ennishill would become a brand ambassador in february  santander was announced as the new sponsor of transport for londons bicycle hire scheme branded as santander cycles santander replaced barclays as title sponsor see alsoedit companies portal banking in the united kingdom list of banks in the united kingdom referencesedit  a b c d annual report  pdf santander uk plc march    ward map london borough of camden retrieved on  may   registered office details archive santander uk retrieved on  may  santander uk plc registered office  triton square regent’s place london nw an united kingdom  christie sophie  august  how good is your banks customer service retrieved  january    how do you rate your bank account  february  retrieved  july    financial research survey  july  retrieved  july    uk financial firms downgraded by moodys rating agency bbc news  october  retrieved  march    qa is santander uk a safe bank bbc news  june  retrieved  march    al shareholders approve takeover bbc news  septe